<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Área de Expertos — ExpertHour</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --cream: #F5F0E8;
  --ink: #1A1612;
  --ink-light: #4A4540;
  --ink-faint: #8A8580;
  --gold: #B8A06A;
  --border: #E0D8CC;
  --white: #FFFFFF;
}
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
body { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; background: var(--ink); min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

header {
  padding: 0 40px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  height: 64px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
}

.logo {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--white);
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.logo span { color: var(--gold); }

.main {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 60px 20px;
}

.container {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 480px;
  text-align: center;
}

.eyebrow {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.title {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 40px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--white);
  line-height: 1.15;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.desc {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
}

.cards {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  padding: 28px 20px;
  text-align: center;
  text-decoration: none;
  display: block;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--gold);
  transform: scaleX(0);
  transition: transform 0.2s;
}

.card:hover {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  border-color: rgba(184,160,106,0.4);
}

.card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }

.card-icon {
  font-size: 28px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  display: block;
}

.card-title {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--white);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.card-desc {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.card.primary {
  background: var(--gold);
  border-color: var(--gold);
}

.card.primary:hover {
  background: #C9B07A;
  border-color: #C9B07A;
}

.card.primary::before { display: none; }

.card.primary .card-title { color: var(--ink); }
.card.primary .card-desc { color: rgba(26,22,18,0.65); }

.divider {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.divider-line {
  flex: 1;
  height: 1px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
}

.divider-text {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.info-box {
  background: rgba(184,160,106,0.08);
  border: 1px solid rgba(184,160,106,0.2);
  padding: 20px 24px;
  text-align: left;
}

.info-title {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--gold);
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.info-text {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  line-height: 1.7;
}

.info-text a {
  color: var(--gold);
  text-decoration: none;
}

.info-text a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

footer {
  padding: 24px 40px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  text-align: center;
}

.footer-text {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  header { padding: 0 20px; }
  .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .title { font-size: 32px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <a href="https://expertos.experthour.co" class="logo">Expert<span>Hour</span></a>
</header>

<main class="main">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Portal de expertos</p>
    <h1 class="title">Bienvenido,<br>colega experto.</h1>
    <p class="desc">Gestiona tus solicitudes de sesión desde tu correo. Cuando un cliente solicite una asesoría contigo, recibirás un email con todos los detalles.</p>

    <div class="cards">
      <a href="https://aguileracisf.typeform.com/to/cfr8AP9G" class="card primary" target="_blank">
        <span class="card-icon">✦</span>
        <div class="card-title">Quiero ser experto</div>
        <div class="card-desc">Regístrate y empieza a monetizar tu conocimiento</div>
      </a>
      <a href="mailto:expertos@experthour.co" class="card">
        <span class="card-icon">✉</span>
        <div class="card-title">Contactar soporte</div>
        <div class="card-desc">¿Tienes una duda sobre una sesión?</div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="divider">
      <div class="divider-line"></div>
      <span class="divider-text">¿Ya eres experto?</span>
      <div class="divider-line"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
      <div class="info-title">Cómo gestionar tus sesiones</div>
      <div class="info-text">
        Cuando un cliente solicite una sesión contigo, recibirás un email en tu correo con todos los detalles de la consulta. Responde ese email para aceptar o rechazar la solicitud.<br><br>
        ¿No recibes notificaciones? Escríbenos a <a href="mailto:expertos@experthour.co">expertos@experthour.co</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  <p class="footer-text">© 2025 ExpertHour · Bogotá, Colombia · <a href="https://expertos.experthour.co" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);text-decoration:none">expertos.experthour.co</a></p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
